text: <@U2DTF0B6Y|lizrhodes> pinned a message to this channel.

It is that time of year again! Uncorked is going bowling and we are saying goodbye to the AMF 300 Lanes. We are so sad to see it go, but we get one last chance to say goodbye!

And...We get to introduce our interns to some Uncorked traditions, too!

Rollers Retreat Bowling
Thursday, July 20, 2017
5:30 to 8:30 pm
@AMF 300 Lanes 

Excited that Uncorked is sponsoring this opportunity to hang out together, get to know our interns a little more, and have a great time wearing ugly shoes!

Bowling Logistics
Please RSVP here by Friday, July 14th
We'll set up teams in another form once we know who is going!
Bowling starts at 5:30 pm, get in a little early grab your shoes and get to your lane!
Shoe rental is included.
Food and Drinks will be provided (We got a mix of everything)
Don't forget your socks!
Travel Logistics

Please be aware that staff is individually responsible for transportation there and back. We suggest that you carpool! 

Join <#C650RRB7D|rollersretreat2017> channel on slack
